: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen one of you yawns in the prayer, let him restrain it as much as he can, lest Satan enter therein.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2995 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15930,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/09\/05\/salat-al-jamaah-fard-kifayah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34722,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Community: Devil attacks the isolated sheep","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported:\u00a0The\u00a0Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf three people in a town or in the desert do not establish prayer among them, then Satan has overcome them. You must establish the congregation, for the wolf eats the isolated\u00a0sheep.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 547 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3085,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/28\/shaytan-flees-from-adhan\/","url_meta":{"origin":34722,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Adhan: Satan runs away from the call to prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 28, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, 